    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="LaTeX-常见命令总结"><a href="#LaTeX-常见命令总结" class="headerlink" title="LaTeX 常见命令总结"></a>LaTeX 常见命令总结</h3><p>为了帮助你更好地使用 LaTeX，这里总结了一些常见的命令和基本的 LaTeX 文档结构。你可以根据这些内容开始编写你的文档。</p><h4 id="1-基本的-LaTeX-文档结构"><a href="#1-基本的-LaTeX-文档结构" class="headerlink" title="1. 基本的 LaTeX 文档结构"></a>1. 基本的 LaTeX 文档结构</h4><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\documentclass</span>&#123;article&#125;   <span class="hljs-comment">% 文档类型，这里选择的是 article</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>[utf8]&#123;inputenc&#125;  <span class="hljs-comment">% 输入文件的编码方式</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>&#123;amsmath&#125;         <span class="hljs-comment">% 数学公式包</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>&#123;graphicx&#125;        <span class="hljs-comment">% 插入图片包</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>&#123;hyperref&#125;        <span class="hljs-comment">% 生成目录、交叉引用的超链接</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\title</span>&#123;你的标题&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\author</span>&#123;你的名字&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\date</span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">\today</span>&#125;                <span class="hljs-comment">% 生成当前日期</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;document&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\maketitle</span>                 <span class="hljs-comment">% 生成标题</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\tableofcontents</span>           <span class="hljs-comment">% 生成目录</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\section</span>&#123;引言&#125;<br>这是引言部分的内容。<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\section</span>&#123;正文&#125;<br>这是正文部分的内容。<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\subsection</span>&#123;数学公式&#125;<br>这是一个行内公式 <span class="hljs-built_in">$</span>E=mc<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>2<span class="hljs-built_in">$</span>。<br><br>这是一个行间公式：<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\[</span><br>E = mc<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>2<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\]</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\subsection</span>&#123;图片&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;figure&#125;[h]<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\centering</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\includegraphics</span>[width=0.5<span class="hljs-keyword">\textwidth</span>]&#123;example.jpg&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\caption</span>&#123;这是图片的说明。&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\label</span>&#123;fig:example&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;figure&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\section</span>&#123;结论&#125;<br>这是结论部分的内容。<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;document&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-常见命令和用法"><a href="#2-常见命令和用法" class="headerlink" title="2. 常见命令和用法"></a>2. 常见命令和用法</h4><ul><li><p><strong>文档类和导言区</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\documentclass</span>&#123;article&#125;   <span class="hljs-comment">% 文章</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\documentclass</span>&#123;report&#125;    <span class="hljs-comment">% 报告</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\documentclass</span>&#123;book&#125;      <span class="hljs-comment">% 书籍</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>导入包</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>[utf8]&#123;inputenc&#125; <span class="hljs-comment">% 字符编码</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>&#123;amsmath&#125;        <span class="hljs-comment">% 数学公式</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>&#123;graphicx&#125;       <span class="hljs-comment">% 图片插入</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>&#123;hyperref&#125;       <span class="hljs-comment">% 超链接</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>标题和作者信息</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\title</span>&#123;文档标题&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\author</span>&#123;作者名&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\date</span>&#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">\today</span>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>生成标题</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\maketitle</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>生成目录</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\tableofcontents</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>章节和子章节</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\section</span>&#123;章节标题&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\subsection</span>&#123;子章节标题&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\subsubsection</span>&#123;次子章节标题&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>插入数学公式</strong></p><ul><li><p>行内公式：<code>$ E=mc^2 $</code></p></li><li><p>行间公式：</p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\[</span><br>E = mc<span class="hljs-built_in">^</span>2<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\]</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>插入图片</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\begin</span>&#123;figure&#125;[h]<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\centering</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\includegraphics</span>[width=0.5<span class="hljs-keyword">\textwidth</span>]&#123;example.jpg&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\caption</span>&#123;图片说明&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">\label</span>&#123;fig:example&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\end</span>&#123;figure&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>引用图片、表格、公式等</strong></p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex">参考图 <span class="hljs-keyword">\ref</span>&#123;fig:example&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p><strong>生成 PDF 并查看</strong></p><ul><li>确保默认编译器设置为 <code>XeLaTeX</code>，点击编译按钮即可生成 PDF。</li><li>清理辅助文件可以通过 <code>工具</code> &gt; <code>清理辅助文件</code>。</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="常见问题及解决"><a href="#常见问题及解决" class="headerlink" title="常见问题及解决"></a>常见问题及解决</h3><ul><li><p><strong>中文显示问题</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>在导言区添加 <code>ctex</code> 包：</p>  <figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex"><span class="hljs-keyword">\documentclass</span>&#123;article&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>[utf8]&#123;inputenc&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">\usepackage</span>&#123;ctex&#125;         <span class="hljs-comment">% 中文支持</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>选择合适的编译器</strong>：</p><ul><li><code>XeLaTeX</code> 是一个不错的选择，因为它对中文支持较好。</li><li>可以在 <code>选项</code> &gt; <code>TeXStudio 设置</code> &gt; <code>构建</code> 中设置默认编译器为 <code>XeLaTeX</code>。</li></ul></li></ul><p>通过这些设置和命令，你应该能够更好地开始使用 LaTeX 进行文档编写。如果有任何问题，请随时告诉我。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
